data.description: Back on market due to no fault from seller.     This 3 bedroom 2 1/2 bath is located on a quiet cul-de-sac in beautiful Dover Delaware.  Many upgrades within the last year include siding, windows, Newer HVAC, deck and rails and new flooring throughout home.  Updated kitchen incudes all new stainless-steel appliances, plenty of cabinet and granite counter space with a large island.  Kitchen also boasts an integrated desk/office space. The double opening French doors open to a spacious deck with a partial overhang covering approximately 20% of deck and ready for TV mount (included).  Also included is a motion sensor light.  The  backyard is also fenced in with entrances on both sides of house, one side is removable to accommodate a vehicle for entry.  Lots of room for all and for entertaining friends. There is a finished basement with two large bonus rooms for additional bedrooms or your preferred use. This additional finished area allows for over approximately 2000 square feet of living space.   So much to see so make your appointment today!
